<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cardamomo Box Lab — Regalos con intención</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Crea tu caja de regalo perfecta. Elige cada producto, personaliza tu mensaje y sorprende a quien más quieres." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,300;9..40,400;9..40,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --cream: #faf7f2;
      --cream-dark: #f2ede4;
      --tan: #e8ddd0;
      --brown: #7a5c3e;
      --brown-dark: #5c4230;
      --text: #2c2420;
      --text-muted: #8a7a6e;
      --border: rgba(122,92,62,0.15);
      --white: #ffffff;
      --shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(122,92,62,0.10);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 200;
      background: rgba(250,247,242,0.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      height: 64px;
    }
    
    .cart-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--brown);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 8px 18px 8px 14px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background-color: var(--cream-dark);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: var(--brown-dark);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* LAYOUT */
    .lab-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .sticky-preview {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: static; 
    }

    .box-visualizer {
      width: 100%;
      height: 250px;
      background: var(--cream-dark);
      border: 2px dashed var(--text-muted);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .steps-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .step-section {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .step-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--brown-dark);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* GRID DE OPCIONES */
    .options-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .option-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--cream);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border 0.3s;
    }
    .option-card:hover { border-color: var(--brown); }

    /* CONTROLES DE CANTIDAD */
    .qty-control {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .qty-btn {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--brown-dark);
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .qty-btn:hover { background: var(--tan); }

    /* FORMULARIOS Y CHECKBOXES */
    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .form-group label { color: var(--text); font-size: 14px; }
    
    .checkout-btn {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--brown-dark);
      color: var(--white);
      border: none;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE ESCRITORIO */
    @media (min-width: 992px) {
      .lab-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 400px 1fr;
        align-items: start;
      }
      .sticky-preview {
        position: sticky;
        top: 96px; 
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="brand-logo">
      <span style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--brown-dark);">CARDAMOMO BOX LAB</span>
    </div>
    <button class="cart-btn">Mi Caja <span style="background: white; color: var(--brown); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px;">0</span></button>
  </nav>

  <header class="hero">
    <h1>Regalos con Intención</h1>
    <p>Te damos la bienvenida al laboratorio de Cardamomo. Aquí no enviamos simples regalos; creas experiencias únicas. Elige el tamaño de tu caja, selecciona productos especiales, añade un toque de color y escribe una dedicatoria inolvidable.</p>
  </header>

  <main class="lab-layout">
    
    <aside class="box-preview-container">
      <div class="sticky-preview">
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Tu Caja Cardamomo</h3>
        <div class="box-visualizer">
          <p>[ Vista Previa de la Caja ]</p>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1rem; font-size: 14px;">
          <p style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;"><span>Productos:</span> <strong>0</strong></p>
          <p style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;"><span>Empaque:</span> <strong>$0 MXN</strong></p>
          <p style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;"><span>Envío:</span> <strong style="color: var(--brown);">¡Gratis!</strong></p>
          <p style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--brown-dark);"><span>Total:</span> <strong>$0.00 MXN</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="steps-container">
      
      <section id="paso-1" class="step-section">
        <h2>1. Elige el tamaño de tu caja</h2>
        <div class="options-grid">
          <div class="option-card">
            <div style="height: 100px; background: var(--cream-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">[ Img Caja Chica ]</div>
            <strong style="display: block;">Caja Chica</strong>
            <span style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted);">Medidas: 30x20x10 cm<br>Ideal para 2-4 productos</span>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--brown-dark);"><strong>$70 MXN</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="option-card">
            <div style="height: 100px; background: var(--cream-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">[ Img Caja Grande ]</div>
            <strong style="display: block;">Caja Grande</strong>
            <span style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted);">Medidas: 30x30x10 cm<br>Ideal para 4-8 productos</span>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--brown-dark);"><strong>$80 MXN</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="paso-2" class="step-section">
        <h2>2. Elige el color de tu listón</h2>
        <div class="options-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(120px, 1fr));">
          <div class="option-card" style="padding: 1rem;"><div style="width: 30px; height: 30px; background: #9CAF88; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;"></div><span style="font-size: 13px;">Verde Salvia</span></div>
          <div class="option-card" style="padding: 1rem;"><div style="width: 30px; height: 30px; background: #C5837A; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;"></div><span style="font-size: 13px;">Rosa Polvo</span></div>
          <div class="option-card" style="padding: 1rem;"><div style="width: 30px; height: 30px; background: #EAE0D5; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;"></div><span style="font-size: 13px;">Crema Marfil</span></div>
          <div class="option-card" style="padding: 1rem;"><div style="width: 30px; height: 30px; background: #3B3A3A; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;"></div><span style="font-size: 13px;">Negro Suave</span></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="paso-3" class="step-section">
        <h2>3. Agrega tus productos</h2>
        <div class="options-grid">
          
          <div class="option-card">
            <div style="height: 120px; background: var(--cream-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">[ Img Producto ]</div>
            <strong>Vino Cune Crianza</strong>
            <p style="color: var(--brown-dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">$329 MXN</p>
            <div class="qty-control">
              <button class="qty-btn">-</button>
              <span>0</span>
              <button class="qty-btn">+</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="option-card">
            <div style="height: 120px; background: var(--cream-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">[ Img Producto ]</div>
            <strong>Chocolate Culto</strong>
            <p style="color: var(--brown-dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">$249 MXN</p>
            <div class="qty-control">
              <button class="qty-btn">-</button>
              <span>0</span>
              <button class="qty-btn">+</button>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="paso-4" class="step-section">
        <h2>4. Detalles finales y Pago</h2>
        
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Mensaje personalizado (Opcional)</h4>
          <textarea placeholder="Ej: ¡Feliz cumpleaños! Espero que disfrutes cada detalle..." style="width: 100%; height: 80px; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: inherit;"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem; background: var(--cream-dark); border-radius: 8px;">
          <h4 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Método de Pago</h4>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="radio" id="pago-tarjeta" name="metodo_pago" value="tarjeta">
            <label for="pago-tarjeta">Tarjeta de Crédito / Débito</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="radio" id="pago-transferencia" name="metodo_pago" value="transferencia">
            <label for="pago-transferencia">Transferencia Bancaria (SPEI)</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="checkbox" id="aviso-privacidad" required>
            <label for="aviso-privacidad">He leído y acepto el <a href="#" style="color: var(--brown-dark);">Aviso de Privacidad</a>.*</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="checkbox" id="newsletter">
            <label for="newsletter">Quiero recibir promociones y novedades de Cardamomo Box Lab.</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="checkout-btn">Finalizar Pedido</button>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>